ntent/uploads/2025/04/samsung-s25-edge-cad-pricing-bluesky-post.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/samsung-s25-edge-cad-pricing-bluesky-post.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe pricing was originally spotted by Bluesky user \u003ca href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/rquandt.bsky.social/post/3lnkzrgzcak24\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eRoland Quandt\u003c/a\u003e when he was searching through the terms and conditions of the offer on the French version of the Canadian site (most businesses have both an English and French version of their websites in Canada). We were able to confirm the pricing ourselves. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eAccording to the listing, the 256GB variant is priced at $1,678 CAD ($1,200 USD), while the 512GB version goes for $1,858 CAD ($1,400 USD). Those numbers seem to match with earlier reports these would be premium devices. \u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/galaxy-s-25-edge-french-canada-pricing.jpg\" data-img-desc=\"\u0026#34;Source: \u0026lt;a href=\\\u0026#34;https:\\/\\/www.samsung.com\\/ca_fr\\/offer\\/mobile-terms-and-conditions\\/\\\u0026#34; rel=\\\u0026#34;noopener noreferrer\\\u0026#34; target=\\\u0026#34;_blank\\\u0026#34;\u0026gt;Samsung Canada\u0026lt;\\/a\u0026gt;\u0026#34;\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/galaxy-s-25-edge-french-canada-pricing.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/galaxy-s-25-edge-french-canada-pricing.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/galaxy-s-25-edge-french-canada-pricing.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/galaxy-s-25-edge-french-canada-pricing.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/galaxy-s-25-edge-french-canada-pricing.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/galaxy-s-25-edge-french-canada-pricing.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/galaxy-s-25-edge-french-canada-pricing.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/galaxy-s-25-edge-french-canada-pricing.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"3972\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A screenshot of the Galaxy S25 Edge pricing from the French terms and conditions of the Samsung Canada site. \" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/galaxy-s-25-edge-french-canada-pricing.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/galaxy-s-25-edge-french-canada-pricing.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eKorean pricing for the same models surfaced just hours before the leak on the Canadian site, although these were slightly cheaper, at $1,049 and $1,140 USD, respectively. It\u0026#39;s unclear where US pricing will ultimately land, but it\u0026#39;s a safe bet it will be more than $1,000. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch3 id=\"may-13-launch-event-confirmed\"\u003e\n            May 13 launch event confirmed\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe know Samsung is set to unveil the Galaxy S25 Edge at a special event on May 13, and it should become available soon after. Korean sales are expected to begin May 23, followed by a US, and a Canadian, launch on May 30.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003e\nAll that\u0026#39;s left is the official announcement now that pricing is out in the open. Expect Samsung to lean heavily into its premium design and the inevitable    \n\n        \n\u003cspan data-id=\"1025772\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/disable-ai-on-android/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAI features\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n to justify the premium price tag.     \u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n    \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"4882-4bb5-a3cb101f23ca\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/samsung-galaxy-s25-edge-reasons-itll-succeed/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/samsung-galaxy-s25-edge-hands-on-at-unpacked-3.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n        